[src:nixos/manual-nixos-p05] On iOS, background sync is achieved via a silent notification sent by the server every 30 minutes that allows the phone to sync for about 30 seconds, enough for all but the largest videos to be synced on background (if the app is brought to foreground though, sync will resume as normal).
